high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the wall, turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, head towards the sink, turn right towards the window, turn right towards the table.
Cut the apple on the table in three pieces.
Turn left towards the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave and close it.
Turn around and head towards the table.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Turn around and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple slice in it, heat it up, and take it out.
Head towards the sink on your right.
Place the slice of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the slice of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the end counter top on your right.
Pick up the knife.
Turn right and move to the other side of the peninsula just to the left of the knife.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Go right and around the peninsula to the microwave across the room.
Put the knife in the microwave and close the door.
Turn around and go back around the peninsula, stopping to the left of the knife.
Pick up one third of the apple.
Go right and then around the peninsula to the microwave across the room.
Put the apple in the microwave to the left of the glass, cook the apple for a few seconds and remove the apple from the microwave.
Move to the sink on your right.
Put the apple in the right front corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place cooked one third apple into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the end of the counter, face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Take the knife from the counter.
Go straight, turn right at the sink, go straight and around the counter in between the window and the counter, face the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Go around the counter to the right and straight to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go straight and around the counter in between the window and the counter, face the counter.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Go around the counter to the right and straight to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a sink.
